Haryana
Nov 01, 2014
Murder
Description:
			A day after he went missing, an 8-year-old boy was found murdered today at Durga Builder ground.

Police have registered a case of murder against unknown accused and are investigating the matter.

Rohit (alias Golu) went missing after he went to a fair with his friends yesterday.

According to the police, Ajab Singh, a resident of Shivam Colony, Ismailpur had lodged a missing complaint after Rohit did not return home last night.


